name: Silver Google
description:
Just a little Google's start page restyling.

Google's logo and Background image are owned by their owners! Not me :)
additional_info:
2014-02-14:
- Domain replaced with RegExp. Now it should work for any country ('.fr', '.co.uk', '.com.ua' etc.)

2014-02-13:
- Fixed unsecure https status. All images placed right in css as base64 strings.
- Removed annoying Chrome banner for Firefox
- Mirrored on GitHub: http://github.com/sbriskin/userstyles.org

2014-02-12:
- Google's logo was unavailable. Now both images (logo & background) hosted on my own server.
- Logo size decreased to 50%
- Added https://encrypted.google.com search page.

2013-10-30:
- Fixed google's services incorrect icons

2013-10-16:
- Fixed problem with logo at Google.com
- Fixed background URL
